data.text: @chachatowel Pfizer - at least that’s what all of us got yesterday

@KailieACrosby This is good to know! I got first dose AZ Mar 25 and was told by workplace they would not be doing second dose AZ through workplace despite it saying that on Fraser Health site. Now trying to figure out how to get 2nd as AZ which is my preferred. Will look into this clinic!
There is a clinic doing walk-in second does in Surrey for those vaccinated before April 15. Super well organized, friendly staff. In and out in 30 minutes
